==Tagnawt==
Ṣaḥariǧ tezga-d deg yirebbi n wedrar n [[Ǧerǧer]], anda tella tqacuct tunnigt [[Yemma Xliǧa]] (2308 m), imezdaɣ n Ṣaḥariǧ qqaren-as '''Tamguṭ'''.
  
Tagnawt deg tɣiwant-agi d tin yeḥman deg unebdu, d tasemmaḍt s waṭas n ugeffur deg tegrest.

=Amesni (Transport)=
Taɣiwant n Ṣaḥariǧ yezger seg-s ubrid aɣelnaw U°30 i yeqnen [[Imceddalen]] ɣer [[Tanebḍit n Tizi Wezzu|Tizi Wezzu]] akked ubrid amecṭuḥ U°9 i yeqnen Ṣaḥariǧ ɣer [[Aɣbalu|Sellum]] deg taɣiwant n waɣbalu.

