=Tamerrit (Tourisme)=
Taɣiwant n Ṣaḥariǧ tezga-d deg yirebbi n wedrar n [[Ǧerǧer]], dacu i tt-yeǧǧan tesɛa aṭas n yimuḍaq n tmerrit. Gar-asen nezmer ad nadder :<br/>
*[[Tala Rana]] : D tiẓgi tazegzawt deg wedrar n Ǧerǧer, teččur d iɣbula n waman d tliwa, deg-s mazal ttidiren waṭas n yiɣersiwen izagiren, imɣan d isekla yurzen s ngar. 
*[[Yemma Xliǧa]] (tamguṭ) 2308 m : Taqacuct tunnigt deg wedrar n Ǧerǧer.
*[[Tizi n Kulal]] (1500 m) : Tezga-d deg talast ger-as d [[Tanebḍit n Tizi Wezzu|tnebḍit n Tizi Wezzu]].<br/>

Deg yiseggasen-agi ineggura, ama d tagrest neɣ d anebdu, aṭas n yemdanen d twaculin i d-yettasen seg yal tama ɣer tɣiwant n Ṣaḥariǧ akken ad zṛen imuḍaq-agi n tmerrit, ladɣa widak iḥemlen tawennaṭ d tulin n yidurar.

